{
  "stem": "4361.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes but always, it was happening somewhere else.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And this was not yet war.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was in the '30s when Hitler took over.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then, I remember very clearly, for instance, the Evian Conference.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "At the time-- that happened in 1936.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Now at the time, I was only 11 years old and clearly not involved in politics, but rather involved in my studies and being quote, 'a nice girl,' playing the piano, and-- and-- and going to my French teacher, and so forth.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But I do remember my elders talking about the Evian Conference, that Roosevelt-- I mean, he was considered the messiah, or the saint, or the savior-- is going to put an end to this madman.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And there was this Evian Conference.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "That's all I remember.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Next thing I remember was when-- I believe it was the Munich Conference when Daladier, Chamberlain, Mussolini, and Hitler met.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I believe it was in Munich.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I believe in 1938-- I am not sure about the date-- but this is when it began, the chopping up of the various countries.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Namely, they gave Sudetenland to Germany.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And so I remember a magazine, the front page, a four clover leaf.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And in each section of the four-- of-- of-- of the leaf of the clover, there was one Daladier, one Chamberlain, one Hitler, and one Mussolini.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Peace-- it's going to be peace.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My personal experience was none because my life was not affected.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I still had my piano lessons.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I still went for my French lessons, which were aside of the school curriculum.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The Shabbats were still maintained.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The business was going on.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "My brothers eventually got married.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But this was somewhere else, and there was Roosevelt and the West.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
